<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
    <style>
        /* 1. PAPER GRAIN TEXTURE */
        .bg-noise {
            background-color: #F9FAFB;
            background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 200 200' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noiseFilter'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.65' numOctaves='3' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noiseFilter)' opacity='0.05'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
        }

        /* 2. Black Monochrome Gradient */
        .text-gradient {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #000000, #4B5563);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        /* 3. Soft Glow */
        .soft-glow {
            box-shadow: 0 40px 80px -20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .fade-in { animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out forwards; opacity: 0; }
        .fade-in-delayed { animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out 0.3s forwards; opacity: 0; }
        
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-noise text-gray-800 flex flex-col min-h-screen overflow-x-hidden">

    <%- include('partials/nav') %>

    <main class="flex-grow container mx-auto px-5 md:px-8 mt-32 mb-2">
        
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12 relative z-10 fade-in">
            
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-white border border-gray-200 shadow-sm mb-6">
                <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-black"></span>
                <span class="text-[10px] md:text-xs font-bold text-gray-900 tracking-widest uppercase">Our Mission</span>
            </div>

            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-gray-900 tracking-tight leading-[1.1] mb-6">
                A space for <br class="hidden md:block" />
                <span class="text-gradient">thoughtful conversation.</span>
            </h1>

            <p class="text-base md:text-xl text-gray-500 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                We believe that everyone has a story worth telling. Our mission is to provide a minimalist, distraction-free environment for writers and readers to connect.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-20 relative fade-in-delayed">
            <div class="absolute -top-20 -left-20 w-80 h-80 bg-gray-200 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-50 hidden md:block"></div>
            <div class="absolute -bottom-20 -right-20 w-80 h-80 bg-gray-300 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-50 hidden md:block"></div>

            <div class="relative bg-white p-2 md:p-3 rounded-[2rem] soft-glow border border-white">
                <img 
                    src="/images/about.avif" 
                    alt="Minimal Office" 
                    class="rounded-[1.5rem] w-full h-64 md:h-[500px] object-cover grayscale-[20%]"
                >
                
                <div class="relative md:absolute md:bottom-8 md:left-12 -mt-8 md:mt-0 mx-4 md:mx-0 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-xl p-6 md:p-8 rounded-2xl md:rounded-3xl shadow-xl border border-white/50 max-w-md z-10">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-2 md:mb-3">Focus on what matters.</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
                        In a world full of noise, we offer silence. No intrusive ads, no cluttered sidebarsâ€”just your words on a clean digital canvas.
