                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Lightning fast. Your stories load instantly, anywhere in the world. No bloat, just content.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="p-6 md:p-8 rounded-3xl bg-white border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group">
